snippet.title: Red Dead Redemption 2: Official Trailer #2
snippet.description: The all-new trailer for Red Dead Redemption 2, the story of outlaw Arthur Morgan and the Van der Linde gang as they rob, fight and steal their way across the vast and rugged heart of America in order to survive. Coming October 26, 2018 to PlayStation systems.
